data.title: Awful. Rufest owner ever. Never nrver visit the place again
data.text: Manager was out of control and drunk. Drinking with clients all night. Foul language. Rude . Never waste your money there. This place was a decent place now is just trash

data.title: Visited the restaurant as part of a Tapas night
data.text: Very attentive, pleasant, and efficient. Great roast beef with veggies low key environment, basic table set up. Good food at reasonable price.

data.title: Great place for Taco Tuesday
data.text: Been to Duke's several times, great lunch and dinner spot, atmosphere of a sports bar, you can enjoy watching your favorite sporting event, also they have a pool table and darts as well, as mentioned in the title great for taco Tuesday.

data.title: Cheap and Cheerful
data.text:
Nice little place for a casual sandwich or burger and fries. 
Food was tasty, nothing special. No one was given a knife, which was a bit strange but we all had a burger or sandwich, so it was fine. 
Service was great.
Interior was OK, clean which was most important. Some of the booths were sat in the darkness.
The prices were cheap which is always nice. 
Overall a nice experience and would definitely go back.
